com/news/music/red-hot-chili-peppers-californication-video-reaches-over-one-billion-youtube-views-3362659">Red Hot Chili Peppers的“ Californication”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/dr-dres-still-d-r-e-video-hits-one-billion-views-following-super-bowl-performance-3165298">Dre博士的“ Still Dre”</a> ， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/rick-astleys-never-gonna-give-you-up-reaches-one-billion-youtube-views-i-am-kind-of-a-big-deal-3006039">Rick Astley的“永远不会放弃您”</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/cardi-b-celebrates-bodak-yellow-video-reaching-one-billion-youtube-views-3011026">Cardi B的“ Bodak Yellow”</a> 。</p><p>值得注意的是，在去年的<a href="https://www.nme.com/glastonbury-2024">格拉斯顿伯里（Glastonbury）</a>上， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/glastonbury-2024-king-krule-briefly-takes-on-akons-dont-matter-3769865">克鲁尔国王（Krule）进行了简短的封面“无关紧要”</a> 。这并不是马歇尔第一次公开将自己与阿肯联系起来。 In 2018 he admitted that, when being interview whilst drunk, <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/king-krule-interview-drunk-claims-akon-wrote-sonic-hedgehog-theme-2261841">he falsely claimed Akon wrote the Sonic The Hedgehog theme tune.</a></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/features/music-interviews/akon-soundtrack-of-my-life-interview-3459566">在<em>NME</em>的2023年接受Akon的采访中</a>，他透露，这首歌使他哭泣是他的“孤独”。</p><p>他告诉<em>NME</em> ：“当我写它时，我非常孤独。” “当时，由于我自己的不幸和决定，唯一一个有我支持的人不再在我身边。但是对我来说，写这样的歌是一种治疗形式。一旦我拿出来，我感觉好多了。当我看到其他人也可以与之建立联系时，我会再次感觉更好。” </p><figure id="attachment_3470020" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3470020" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3470020" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/akon-getty-MOBO1.jpg" alt="" width="2000" height="1270" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/akon-getty-MOBO1.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/akon-getty-MOBO1-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/07/akon-getty-MOBO1-800x508.jpg 800w, https://w